    "summary": "\u2022\tExperience in the mechanical, electrical, electronic and hydraulic machinery project fields. \n\u2022\tExtensive knowledge in sheet metal machinery, specially in Press-brakes and Guillotine shears. \n\u2022\tConstant monitoring of latest technological trends by visiting international trade fairs and factories of the most important machine and parts manufacturers.\n\u2022\tTechnical consultant from the Brazilian Ministry of Labor and Employment to prepare Annex 8 of NR 12 (safety obligations to be implemented in machines and equipment for commercialization in Brazil).\n\u2022\tCoordinator of the National Committee ABNT CE004-001: 013 \u2013 Press Brakes, which takes care of the translation and adaptation of the EN12622 standard for Brazilian Portuguese.\n\u2022\tContributions: \no\tManagement in engineering, service and production areas; \no\tProduction monitoring and follow-up; \no\tRemote technical support to the factory sales team and on-site client support; \no\tClient Order portfolio administration; \no\tPreparation of cost spreadsheets and management reports; \no\tDirect negotiation with national and international suppliers; \no\tFollow-up on the component and machinery importing with Customs brokers; \no\tMaintenance, service and repair support with internal technicians and external service providers in Brazil and abroad. \no\tAdministration of technical training for customers; \no\tElaboration of operation and instruction manuals for the company manufactured products;\no\tDraft and design of mechanical, hydraulic and electrical machinery projects with AutoCAD and SolidWorks; \no\tDevelopment of special tools and machinery according to customer\u2019s specific product needs; \no\tStartup and commissioning of CNC machinery; \no\tPLC Software development; \no\tFollow-up and participation in retrofitting of several machines; \no\tAid in preparation of booths and active participation in several trade fairs.\n",
